The paper deals with pose transfer between human meshes, which involves computer vision (CV) and graphics (GR) techniques. The proposed model leverages deep learning techniques, which falls under machine learning (MM) and artificial intelligence (AI) categories. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV and cs.GR, followed by cs.MM, cs.LG, and cs.AI.
